Package: dnd5e
Title: D&D 5e data
Version: 0.4
Authors@R: person("Jarad", "Niemi", email = "niemi@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains data and functions for D&D 5e. The data include equipment (armor, gear, weapons), monsters, and spells. The functions help the Dungeon Master organize the information needed for a particular campaign or encounter.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Suggests:
    rvest,
    dplyr,
    readr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
